OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBenefits rules changed for 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fterminally ill claimants   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Fast-tracked access to benefits for    
OL,6, those with terminal illness will be    
OL,7, doubled from six months to one year.   
OL,9,FThe changes will come into operation in
OL,10,FApril 2022.                            
OL,12,FCurrently patients have to prove they  
OL,13,Fhave less than six months to live to   
OL,14,Faccess a fast-tracked scheme for       
OL,15,Funiversal credit, and employment and   
OL,16,Fsupport allowance.                     
OL,18,FFollowing reports by the BBC in June   
OL,19,F2021, the government promised to       
OL,20,Faddress the issue.                     
